    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for your dream ride? This car is an absolute gem and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure driving bliss. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019ve really gotta see it to believe it! Perfect for anyone who wants that brand-new feel without the brand-new price tag. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
