    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a superlative example of the E46 chassis. This S54-powered masterpiece features a high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, benefiting from proactive rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul. The power is transmitted through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been professionally reinforced at the subframe mounting points to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Handling is sharpened by Bilstein PSS10 adjustable coilovers and refreshed polyurethane bushings throughout. The exterior retains its factory-original paint depth, and the cabin is free of typical Nappa leather wear. This is a zero-fault, turn-key machine for the performance-driven collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
