    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained since day one. Finished in a stunning metallic gloss that retains its deep, factory luster, the exterior is entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating and a lifetime of exclusive hand-washing. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery shows absolutely no bolster wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed solely by certified master technicians and a drive that feels tight, responsive, and powerful. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle is ready for a private collection or the open road.",
      "price": 48500.0,
